data.title: WUSA 9 Allyson Rae Social Media Sweepstakes Rules
data.meta_description: WUSA 9 Allyson Rae Social Media Sweepstakes Rules - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document outlines the official rules for the WUSA 9 Allyson Rae Social Media Sweepstakes. It states that no purchase is necessary to enter, and that the sweepstakes is open to legal US residents over 18 years old. To enter, participants must follow and retweet daily content from Allyson Rae's Twitter account between March 16-20, 2015. One winner will be randomly selected each day who correctly retweets the message, and each winner will receive a $100 Visa gift card. The rules also specify winner notification procedures, prize details, and that the sponsor's decisions are final.
